@yzhliu

This PR fixed a crash issue in running an end-to-end task with TSIM backend.

It takes around 29 M cycles to run resnet18 inference with current Chisel VTA. In addition, because of the multi-threading support (#4491) in simulating Chisel VTA, it only takes 5 min to perform the cycle-accurate simulation on my laptop computer.

